</li>
<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Wisdom#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Glück J (October 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6178965">"Measuring Wisdom: Existing Approaches, Continuing Challenges, and New Developments"</a>. <i>The Journals of Gerontology. Series B, Psychological Sciences and Social Sciences</i>. <b>73</b> (8): 1393–1403. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1093%2Fgeronb%2Fgbx140">10.1093/geronb/gbx140</a>. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>&#160;<span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6178965">6178965</a></span>. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PubMed_Identifier" class="mw-redirect" title="PubMed Identifier">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/29281060">29281060</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Journals+of+Gerontology.+Series+B%2C+Psychological+Sciences+and+Social+Sciences&amp;rft.atitle=Measuring+Wisdom%3A+Existing+Approaches%2C+Continuing+Challenges%2C+and+New+Developments&amp;rft.volume=73&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.pages=1393-1403&amp;rft.date=2018-10&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6178965&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F29281060&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1093%2Fgeronb%2Fgbx140&amp;rft.aulast=Gl%C3%BCck&amp;rft.aufirst=J&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6178965&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AWisdom" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r886058088"/></span>
</li>
